tiaraPppMib.name: tiaraPppMib
tiaraPppMib.contactinfo: Tiara Networks Customer Support 525 Race Street, Suite 100, San Jose, CA 95126 USA Tel: +1 408-216-4700 Fax: +1 408-216-4701 E-mail: support@tiaranetworks.com
tiaraPppMib.description: The MIB module defines the managed objects for Tiara enterrpise PPP/MLPPP.

pppTable.name: pppTable
pppTable.description: This table contains configurable parameters related to PPP/MLPPP bundle.

pppTableEntry.name: pppTableEntry
pppTableEntry.description: An entry in the PPP Table which contains the configuration for a particular bundle instance identified by the bundleId.

pppMtu.name: pppMtu
pppMtu.description: Minimum, default and maximum packet sizes to be sent separated by hyphens.

pppMru.name: pppMru
pppMru.description: Minimum, default and maximum packet sizes to be received separated by hyphens.

mlpppMrru.name: mlpppMrru
mlpppMrru.description: Maximum received reconstructed unit - maximum number of octets in the information fields of reassembled packets. This variable can be set only if the bundle is multi-link.

mlpppSeq.name: mlpppSeq
mlpppSeq.description: MLPPP sequence number length (short = 12 bits ; long = 24 bits. This variable can be set only if the bundle is multi-link.

mlpppSegmentThreshold.name: mlpppSegmentThreshold
mlpppSegmentThreshold.description: Segmentation threshold - number of octets a packet must exceed before being fragmented for transmission. This variable can be set only if the bundle is multi-link.

mlpppDiffDelay.name: mlpppDiffDelay
mlpppDiffDelay.description: Tolerance, in milliseconds, to differential delay between links. If The differential delay exceeds this limit, the corresponding link will be removed from the bundle. This variable can be set only if the bundle is multi-link.

mlpppDiscriminator.name: mlpppDiscriminator
mlpppDiscriminator.description: IP address of MLPPP discriminator. This variable can be set only if the bundle is multi-link.

pppStatsTable.name: pppStatsTable
pppStatsTable.description: This table contains the statistics for PPP/MLPPP bundles.

pppStatsTableEntry.name: pppStatsTableEntry
pppStatsTableEntry.description: An entry in the PPP Statistics Table which contains the statistics for a particular bundle instance identified by the bundleId.

pppStatsBytesRxLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsBytesRxLastBootOrClear
pppStatsBytesRxLastBootOrClear.description: This counter has the number of bytes received on this bundle since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsBytesTxLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsBytesTxLastBootOrClear
pppStatsBytesTxLastBootOrClear.description: This counter has the number of bytes transmitted on this bundle since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsPktsRxLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsPktsRxLastBootOrClear
pppStatsPktsRxLastBootOrClear.description: This counter has the number of packets received on this bundle since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsPktsTxLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsPktsTxLastBootOrClear
pppStatsPktsTxLastBootOrClear.description: This counter has the number of packets transmitted on this bundle since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsErrPktsRxLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsErrPktsRxLastBootOrClear
pppStatsErrPktsRxLastBootOrClear.description: This counter has the number of error packets received on this bundle since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsUpDownStatesLastBootOrClear.name: pppStatsUpDownStatesLastBootOrClear
pppStatsUpDownStatesLastBootOrClear.description: This variable has the count on the number of times this PPP/MLPPP bundle have made the 'Down' to 'Up' and 'Up' to 'Down' transitions since it was last booted or cleared.

pppStatsBytesRxLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsBytesRxLastFiveMins
pppStatsBytesRxLastFiveMins.description: This counter has the number of bytes received on this bundle in the last 5 minutes.

pppStatsBytesTxLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsBytesTxLastFiveMins
pppStatsBytesTxLastFiveMins.description: This counter has the number of bytes transmitted on this bundle in the last 5 minutes.

pppStatsPktsRxLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsPktsRxLastFiveMins
pppStatsPktsRxLastFiveMins.description: This counter has the number of packets received on this bundle in the last 5 minutes.

pppStatsPktsTxLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsPktsTxLastFiveMins
pppStatsPktsTxLastFiveMins.description: This counter has the number of packets transmitted on this bundle in the last 5 minutes.

pppStatsErrPktsRxLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsErrPktsRxLastFiveMins
pppStatsErrPktsRxLastFiveMins.description: This counter has the number of error packets received on this bundle in the last 5 minutes.

pppStatsUpDownStatesLastFiveMins.name: pppStatsUpDownStatesLastFiveMins
pppStatsUpDownStatesLastFiveMins.description: This variable has the count on the number of times this PPP/MLPPP bundle have made the 'Down' to 'Up' and 'Up' to 'Down' transitions in the last 5 minutes.
